{"Sid":0,"Did":126925,"Id":"604564","Title":"員山七賢再興宮舊材再利用","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collection/dc3fadda-9cbc-466e-8d32-c3f5395ab930/109-her-pa-2512-202011141633285faf66a9552b80.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collection/3e9b9fb6-debc-4fed-90c0-cdcb719901e1/109-her-pa-2512-202011141633285faf66a9552b81.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n　　員山七賢再興宮位於員山七賢，背臨蘭陽溪，坐東南朝西北，為單殿式三開間前帶拜亭之廟宇建築。1980年代再次重建時，仍繼續沿用1932（昭和7）年重修時的木作構件。除了部分運用在步口廊員光、門簪以及對看牆腰堵外，亦被再利用於廟內的4扇新設門扇。\n\n　　譬如往側邊廂房太歲殿的門扇，其上部分即運用了兩組的「螭虎團爐」木雕，此組舊構件背面襯以漆以紅色的木板，正面則以玻璃固定。在龍虎兩側神龕旁的門扇，也是再用舊建築之木雕裝飾，上下兩堵為花鳥主題，如「鳳凰牡丹」與「松鶴」；中堵則可能原為束隨的花卉捲草主題木雕；上下堵與中堵間的部分，則填塞以不同形式的柿蒂紋圖案。此外，新設門扇上方的氣窗，亦是再利用舊建築之柿蒂紋圖案木雕。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.742887","Keyword_Latitude":"24.718898","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/2A1D3A10-776C-4C48-97B1-352350B0BBBC","Original_Identifier":"604564","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"木雕 / 昭和 / 螭虎團爐","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2021/01/06 18:53:48","timelines":"","place":"","address":"宜蘭縣員山鄉浮洲路11號","longitude":"121.742887","latitude":"24.718898","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"無","writer":"蔡明志/ 林鴻文","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collectionOpen/eba18494-bcac-45aa-b456-e68caef67dac/109-her-pa-2512-re-202011141635225faf66a9552b80.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collectionOpen/48717249-ca9e-49a4-aa01-d69f543044b8/109-her-pa-2512-re-202011141635225faf6